{"tid":552611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【凍死】元朗逾千條寶石魚反肚　漁戶料蝕50萬","createTime":"2018-02-06T16:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T03:51:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cefffbb6a0c9380826e295f57386ebd9c6478017","tid":552611,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=SlhK5jqiF0g&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSlhK5jqiF0g%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=8QKeduE8D59wrLrvr8TMksmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=82e89bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=SlhK5jqiF0g&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily 觀看次數：120<br />\n已訂閱<br />\n141<br />\n發佈日期：2018年2月6日<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】元朗逢吉鄉一個魚場，自2008年起獲漁護署提供魚苗培育本地寶石魚，近年開始大量繁殖，但寒潮持續個多星期，令大量寶石魚「反肚」死亡，昨更一天內死去千多條，漁戶憂未來幾天2萬條寶石魚凶多吉少，料損失50多萬元，他批評魚類統營處未有應約收走魚穫，影響生計。不過漁護署指該漁戶去年中起已沒有參加有關計劃。"},{"pid":"e9ddf168502326be1ff2c3651a05b4d5be568efb","tid":552611,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"濕凍到魚都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港濕凍地表最凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85aaa8c848c66561f7a22e633690d57f8d91b3c8","tid":552611,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0a4045506b57566dc5936db4b055540a0c0516","tid":552611,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9640b04268e029f63d15d36dc1fd29e1403689","tid":552611,"uid":80966,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f695fd8ec0dc61b41651a92745da4badb78a1932","tid":552611,"uid"